AzureBlade had had no time to intervene. The bot's sentence had 
successfully shook his rage, and he had now been disposed to listen to 
him.

AzureBlade: GOTH! ARE YOU TWISTED?!? WHY DID YOU FIRE ON HIM?!?!

He wanted to rush at him and beat him bad, but, somehow, he held 
himself. He started pacing around furiously. He went to a tree, 
activated his plasma blades from the extended jet wings and reduced it 
to cinders. He had to pass his anger on something.

AzureBlade: Prowl, say something!
